    {
      "title": "Write the ratio equation",
      "content": "The ratio $x$ to $y$ is equivalent to $8$ to $3$, so<br/><br/>$$\\frac{x}{y}=\\frac{8}{3}$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Substitute the given value",
      "content": "Use $x=184$:<br/><br/>$$\\frac{184}{y}=\\frac{8}{3}$$<br/><br/>Cross multiply:<br/><br/>$$8y=184(3)$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve for the missing value",
      "content": "Finish the calculation:<br/><br/>$$8y=552$$<br/>$$y=69$$<br/><br/>The answer is <strong>69</strong>."
